# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Genre mapping
#
# Keys are lowercase Goodreads shelf tags.
# Values are (genre_name, subgenre_name_or_None) using exact DB names.
#
# Genre names (Fiction): Fantasy, Science Fiction, Romance, Crime, Horror, Other
# Genre names (Non-Fiction): Biography, History, Learning, True Crime, Other
#
# Subgenres: see lkup_book_sub_genres — keyed by (genre_name, sub_genre_name).
# Ambiguous subgenre names (e.g. "Contemporary", "Historical", "Paranormal")
# exist under multiple genres, so genre_name is always required.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

